'From Squeak3.1alpha of 4 February 2001 [latest update: #3714] on 24 February 2001 at 6:38:10 pm'!"Change Set:		PublishLight-arDate:			24 February 2001Author:			Andreas RaabRemove project navigation morph before publishing to reduce space usage. An empty project now publishes with approx. 4k."!!ProjectNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'the actions' stamp: 'ar 2/23/2001 21:00'!publishStyle: aSymbol forgetURL: aBoolean	| w |	w _ self world ifNil: [^1 beep].	w setProperty: #SuperSwikiPublishOptions toValue: aSymbol.	self delete.	w project 		storeOnServerShowProgressOn: self 		forgetURL: aBoolean.! !